1ys.png&amp;h=2794d7b6&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\">《方舟投資主禱文》<br />\n我們在天上的母：願人都尊契媽的名為聖。<br />\n願契媽的國降臨，願契媽的電動車馳騁在地上，<br />\n如同爆升在天上。我們盼望的升幅，<br />\n求契媽今日賜給我們，又求饒恕石仔拋售的罪，<br />\n因為我們饒恕得罪SH的人。<br />\n不叫我們遇見破壞性創新，拯救我們脫離短炒。<br />\n離開方舟的叛徒，定必受到地獄之火的懲罰。<br />\n因為坐貨、賺錢、移民，<br />\n全是契媽的子民，直到永遠。阿們。</p><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https://na.cx/i/pyrcfjq.gif&amp;h=9f6bf1e8&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTrello 開左Public美股認真討論區 board，慢慢搬野上去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://trello.com/b/513A9wIT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftrello.com%2Fb%2F513A9wIT&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBQKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=8c677fa8\" target=\"_blank\">https://trello.com/b/513A9wIT</a><br />\n<br />\n開左個美股認真討論區（全民編輯留言區），巴打可以加野上去，周末有空會整理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://trello.com/b/1SNId2E3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftrello.com%2Fb%2F1SNId2E3&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBQKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=d09506f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://trello.com/b/1SNId2E3</a><br />\n<br />\n記得用<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">假名</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://temp-mail.org/en/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftemp-mail.org%2Fen%2F&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBQKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=2d4ae925\" target=\"_blank\">https://temp-mail.org/en/</a><br />\n<br />\n記得要加左下面條link member先可以留言<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://trello.com/invite/b/1SNId2E3/b3210a9ad8d0743204ac005aef0d25d5/%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E8%AA%8D%E7%9C%9F%E8%A8%8E%E8%AB%96%E5%8D%80%EF%BC%88%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E7%B7%A8%E8%BC%AF%E7%95%99%E8%A8%80%E5%8D%80%EF%BC%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/lin